descriptionHtml:
If you want a simple but useful app, a random picker is a great choice.

There are many benefits of using a random picker.

* Decrease decision fatigue
* Increase novelty
* Expand possibilities
* Create serendipity

What is Random Video - Random Picker

Are you a Tony Robbins fan? Already watched the most popular Tony Robbins videos?
Want to find more tony robbins video?
Have fun scrolling. Or...
download and try Random Video.

Random Video, generates a random video. Unlike other random video generators, Random Video
gives you options.

With this random picker you can,

* Customize the type of random videos using keywords
* Create a list of keywords
* Pick a random video related to keywords
* Picker generates only 1 video at a time reducing decision fatigue
* Open and play random video in app
* Video dates range from oldest to latest, offering wide variety of possibilities
* Learn about new topics from a vast library of videos

Download Random Video Picker today and prepare to be discover, learn, and grow with 1 random video
at a time.

For other random picker apps, visit Random Corp's developer page.

title: Random Video - Random Picker

creator: Random Corp - The Random Company
descriptionHtml:
Beceome an explorer

What do you get when you search for videos?

You get videos that have been watched over and over -- and for good reason.

What happens after you watch those?

You get recommended videos related to that one.

There is nothing wrong with walking the well-worn path, especially when you know exactly what you
are looking for.

But what if you don't? What if you are an explorer? What if you crave different?

Well, Random Video - Random Picker is the app you were destined to discover.

Random Video opens up a new road by letting you discover new videos that you wouldn't normally watch.

These videos are the rocks and trees that others pass up. But you are an explorer. You know that
there are diamonds in the rubble waiting to be discovered.

How it Works

This random picker provides all the tools you need to find interesting videos. Just search for
videos by topic. And the apps unique picking strategy will always find you a different video, guaranteed.

So will you keep on the well worn path?

Or will you tread down the unworn path where possibilities abound.


Features

What else can Random Video - Random Picker do,

* Browse for specific topics.

* Rarely generates the same video.

* Find videos you would never be able discovery any way else.
descriptionShort: Outstanding random picker for videos. Explore videos like never before.
